snippet.title: Cladun Returns: This Is Sengoku! - Announcement Trailer (PS4, PS Vita, Steam)
snippet.description:
Website: http://nisamerica.com/games/cladun-returns-sengoku/
Check out the Limited Edition at http://store.nisamerica.com/cladun-returns-sengoku-limited-edition-ps4

The Classic Dungeon series is back! And they're doubling-down on "Classic" with their latest entry, Cladun Returns: This Is Sengoku!

Saddle up for some 8-bit dungeon-crawling goodness with the latest entry in the Cladun series, Cladun Returns: This Is Sengoku! Meet classic heroes from Japan's Sengoku Era as you help the souls of the dead settle their unfinished business.

To learn more, visit http://nisamerica.com/games/cladun-returns-sengoku/ or visit us on Facebook (http://facebook.com/nisamericainc) or Twitter (http://twitter.com/nisamerica)
